videos.description: Iowa State's Abdel Nader catches the inbounds pass and drives into the lane to throw down a strong dunk over an Oklahoma State defender.
videos.headline: Don't try to take a charge when Abdel Nader is flying in

videos.description: Iowa State's Jameel McKay dunks the ball so hard over a defender, it goes off of the Oklahoma State player and comes back out of the hoop, resulting in McKay not getting credit for the basket.
videos.headline: When you dunk it on your opponent's head and don't get two points

videos.description: Standing Ovation for Iowa State's Seniors on Senior Day
videos.headline: Standing Ovation for Iowa State's Seniors on Senior Day

videos.description: Iowa State forward George Niang was a matchup nightmare for Oklahoma State, finishing the home portion of his career with a double-double of 17 points and 10 rebounds.
videos.headline: Niang comes up big for Cyclones on senior night

videos.description: Iowa State forward George Niang gives a classy and emotional speech after the team's win against Oklahoma State on senior night.
